Class BlobServiceOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models.BlobServiceOptions
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AcquireLeaseOptions, CommitBlobBlocksOptions, CopyBlobOptions, CreateBlobBlockOptions, CreateBlobOptions, CreateBlobPagesOptions, CreateBlobSnapshotOptions, CreateContainerOptions, DeleteBlobOptions, DeleteContainerOptions, GetBlobMetadataOptions, GetBlobOptions, GetBlobPropertiesOptions, ListBlobBlocksOptions, ListBlobRegionsOptions, ListBlobsOptions, ListContainersOptions, SetBlobMetadataOptions, SetBlobPropertiesOptions, SetContainerMetadataOptions

    public class BlobServiceOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the base class for options that may be set on Blob Service REST API operations invoked through the BlobContract interface. This class defines a server request timeout, which can be applied to all operations.
